{"tid":1018991,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"熟悉男裝手錶嘅巴絲請入","createTime":"2019-02-12T15:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T00:47:26.000Z","uid":91071,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"48a9254c27a3d73b183d22123bfdf3de49a9a04e","tid":1018991,"uid":91071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:29:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我有一個細佬<br />\n佢好乖 讀u好勤力 又會自己做parttime 搵零用<br />\n所以我好錫佢<br />\n<br />\n佢今年會畢業<br />\n做大佬嘅想送一隻好少少嘅手錶比佢<br />\n但我 自己都係戴seiko 唔捨得<br />\n所以唔係好識牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概幾千蚊度 筆值有限<br />\n<br />\n巴絲打們可否推介一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n形容一下佢<br />\n高 好瘦 戴眼鏡 皮膚白 戴黑框眼鏡<br />\n同埋我知佢鍾意皮革類嘅野<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10d2ff802c88b6a3ddfb7b11bb9213f83836097","tid":1018991,"uid":84840,"like":57,"dislike":10,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:32:27.000Z","msg":"日本 神戶購物街店買<br />\n應該係石英錶<br />\n初步估計可能係d業餘工藝師既手作<br />\n可能係cheap野 所以應該追尋到既機會好細<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg&h=143c908a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg&h=28ad8fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg&h=ad09a2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c45d829e8045c05c2326f1a04f5074e1c181ab91","tid":101899